
DQ (6/5/2008): This is a typical configure command line:
/home/dquinlan/ROSE2/svn-rose/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-boost=/home/dquinlan/local/boost_1_35_0_install --with-ROSE_LONG_MAKE_CHECK_RULE=yes --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE2/ROSE_CompileTree/svn_LINUX-64bit-3.4.6-install

DQ (6/5/2008): With Fortran:
/home/dquinlan/ROSE2/svn-rose/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-boost=/home/dquinlan/local/boost_1_35_0_install --with-ROSE_LONG_MAKE_CHECK_RULE=yes --with-Java=/usr/apps/java/jdk1.5.0_11 --with-JavaJVM=/usr/apps/java/jdk1.5.0_11/jre/lib/amd64/server --with-openFortranParser=/home/dquinlan/ROSE/OpenFortranParser/fortran-parser --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE2/ROSE_CompileTree/svn_LINUX-64bit-3.4.6-fortran_install





OLD CONFIGURE COMMAND LINES:
/home/dquinlan/ROSE/NEW_ROSE/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall -with-CXXFLAGS=-fPIC -with-CFLAGS=-fPIC --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE/ROSE_CompileTree/LINUX-64bit-3.4.6_install CFLAGS=-fPIC CXXFLAGS=-fPIC


With STL debugging:
/home/dquinlan/ROSE/NEW_ROSE/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-ROSE_LONG_MAKE_CHECK_RULE=yes --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall -with-CXXFLAGS="-fPIC -D_GLIBCXX_CONCEPT_CHECKS -D_GLIBCXX_DEBUG" -with-CFLAGS=-fPIC --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE/ROSE_CompileTree/LINUX-64bit-3.4.6_install

Or using the CPPFLAGS variable:
/home/dquinlan/ROSE/NEW_ROSE/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-ROSE_LONG_MAKE_CHECK_RULE=yes --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall --with-CXXFLAGS=-fPIC -with-CFLAGS=-fPIC --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE/ROSE_CompileTree/LINUX-64bit-3.4.6_install CPPFLAGS="-D_GLIBCXX_CONCEPT_CHECKS -D_GLIBCXX_DEBUG" CFLAGS=-fPIC CXXFLAGS=-fPIC


Also use: --enable-rosehpct 
/home/dquinlan/ROSE/NEW_ROSE/configure --with-edg_source_code=true --enable-dq-developer-tests --with-ROSE_LONG_MAKE_CHECK_RULE=yes --enable-rosehpct --with-CXX_DEBUG=-g --with-C_DEBUG=-g --with-CXX_WARNINGS=-Wall --with-CXXFLAGS=-fPIC -with-CFLAGS=-fPIC --prefix=/home/dquinlan/ROSE/ROSE_CompileTree/LINUX-64bit-3.4.6_install CPPFLAGS="-D_GLIBCXX_CONCEPT_CHECKS -D_GLIBCXX_DEBUG" CFLAGS=-fPIC CXXFLAGS=-fPIC



